<div class="_j_content_box">
	        <div id="_j_photo_278442227" data-seq="278442228" data-pid="278442227" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442227.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/4D/wKgBEFpKEVeAITQyAAkiLF4OM-o11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/4D/wKgBEFpKEVeAITQyAAkiLF4OM-o11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442227" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278442229">
            大学期间一个人来过<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>，当时手机支付还不流行，没有现在方便。地铁是两块钱随便坐。现在毕业三年了，男朋友认识两年了，本想一起去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10068.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="哈尔滨" target="_blank">哈尔滨</a>，我们都只有三天假期，很遗憾去不了。两个人再来<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>有新的感觉！<br />
我结合自己的记忆也看了一些游记和攻略，确定了这次的路线。<br />
景点游览地铁一号线最方便，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>南站在地铁四号线，就选了两条地铁交叉的西单站附近的洪城铭豪酒店，基本出门就是大悦城，房价也比较合理。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442235" data-seq="278442236" data-pid="278442235" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442235.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/4F/wKgBEFpKEVqAUk8ZAApDl5t_Ec863.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/4F/wKgBEFpKEVqAUk8ZAApDl5t_Ec863.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442235" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278442237">
            Day1：<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10444.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="青岛" target="_blank">青岛</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>-西单-天安门-王府井-故宫<br />
提前预约顺风车，七点<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10444.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="青岛" target="_blank">青岛</a>火车站出发。<br />
中午到达，半小时到西单站，出门就是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>银行总部，贝律铭老爷子设计的哦，去酒店放下行李我们就出门了。<br />
第一站当然是天安门啦！接着就走到王府井逛了逛！<br />
逛完就去故宫东门的四季民福吃烤鸭去了。话说前面小桌有九十多桌，附近转了一圈回来还有五十桌。从四点半等到了六点半，不过没白等俩小时，服务和菜品都很棒，没受到排队超多的影响。<br />
吃完心满意足，有点冷也有点累就回去休息了。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442239" data-seq="278442240" data-pid="278442239" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
