            <div id="_j_photo_278442251" data-seq="278442252" data-pid="278442251" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442251.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/55/wKgBEFpKEWKAb8CDABI5UYenpaw39.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/55/wKgBEFpKEWKAb8CDABI5UYenpaw39.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442251" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278442257">
            Day2：前门-大栅栏-南锣鼓巷-钟鼓楼-后海-三里屯<br />
大栅栏门框胡<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10435.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="同里" target="_blank">同里</a>面有个百年卤煮老店，果然名不虚传，谦爷每早都要吃的大肠刺身真是不错。<br />
我很喜欢双层巴士，坐在二层前排简直不要太爽！我们坐特11去的南锣鼓巷，等车的空买了鲍老师糕点。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442273" data-seq="278442274" data-pid="278442273" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442273.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/5B/wKgBEFpKEWaAf1btABEoA1MrnPw37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/5B/wKgBEFpKEWaAf1btABEoA1MrnPw37.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442273" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442283" data-seq="278442284" data-pid="278442283" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442283.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/5E/wKgBEFpKEWmAD8_YAA-uthmOWX833.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/5E/wKgBEFpKEWmAD8_YAA-uthmOWX833.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442283" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278442287">
            南锣鼓巷人好多！但是好吃的排队也要买，认准排队人多的准没错！<br />
渴了先来个大杯的老<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>酸梨汤！<br />
蟹黄汤包排队好长！<br />
前一天没吃够，再来一个烤鸭卷！<br />
（味道比四季民福差了不是一点啊）<br />
鼓楼附近有个什么烤串排队好长！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442305" data-seq="278442306" data-pid="278442305" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442305.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/62/wKgBEFpKEWyAF8YAAAk2sQFUlOM48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/62/wKgBEFpKEWyAF8YAAAk2sQFUlOM48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442305" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442340" data-seq="278442341" data-pid="278442340" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442340.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/6E/wKgBEFpKEXKAC_pFABWkPs_kyio46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/6E/wKgBEFpKEXKAC_pFABWkPs_kyio46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442340" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442363" data-seq="278442364" data-pid="278442363" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442363.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/73/wKgBEFpKEXaAKSzrABBsVe2BXfc48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/73/wKgBEFpKEXaAKSzrABBsVe2BXfc48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442363" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278442365">
            买的东西不好拿，先回酒店放下，打车去了三里屯。这个司机好牛啊，这么堵的路他很速度，车技了得！<br />
到了三里屯给我亲爱的买了条围巾，去<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11784.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="莆田" target="_blank">莆田</a>吃的晚饭，菜品其貌不扬，但是原汁原味，简单的食材也能做的味道很惊艳。吃的很香，不愧是米其林一星级餐厅。<br />
吃完逛了逛，想去之前就没捞着去的附近的酒吧看看，the&nbsp;corner什么的，因为门口有一堆一边喝酒一边说胡话的一些外国人被男票拉住不许进了。<br />
之后我们就打车回去了，还是一路堵堵堵。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442385" data-seq="278442386" data-pid="278442385" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442385.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/79/wKgBEFpKEXqAcz39AA46NIn79iM03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/79/wKgBEFpKEXqAcz39AA46NIn79iM03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442385" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442396" data-seq="278442397" data-pid="278442396" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442396.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/7C/wKgBEFpKEX2ADYDTAAgQ6DhVeWc47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/7C/wKgBEFpKEX2ADYDTAAgQ6DhVeWc47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442396" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278442398">
            Day3：景山公园-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10796.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北海" target="_blank">北海</a>公园-琉璃厂<br />
元旦快乐！<br />
（题外话：起床后有朋友问我怎么没去天安门看升国旗，新年第一天很有纪念意义，其实也是国旗护卫队从武警换成解放军的第一天。不好意思的是，我这个人仪式感不强，觉得五点钟早起不如睡到自然醒，你不知道冬天暖和的被窝多么粘人！也许以后有机会去看吧）
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278558888" data-seq="278558889" data-pid="278558888" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278558888.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/10/30/wKgBEFpK2taALrZFAApFEe-i9o030.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/10/30/wKgBEFpK2taALrZFAApFEe-i9o030.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278558888" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442411" data-seq="278442412" data-pid="278442411" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442411.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/7F/wKgBEFpKEYSAAfe9AAzxnIkKr8M47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/7F/wKgBEFpKEYSAAfe9AAzxnIkKr8M47.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442411" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442421" data-seq="278442422" data-pid="278442421" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442421.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/81/wKgBEFpKEYmAJTDBABOl2d9wUo443.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/81/wKgBEFpKEYmAJTDBABOl2d9wUo443.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442421" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278442423">
            吃过早饭去了景山公园，应该是二环以内最高的古建筑吧！门票两元，俯瞰全城（包括故宫、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10796.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北海" target="_blank">北海</a>公园）<br />
景山公园西门出，直走200左右就到了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10796.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北海" target="_blank">北海</a>公园的东门，我太机智了！可惜肚子饿了。中间有个小胡同又有人排队，我跑去一看，是烧饼和鸡腿，我正好饿了，正愁没地吃饭，一样来俩！<br />
之后去了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10796.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北海" target="_blank">北海</a>公园，我发现有滑冰场想去玩玩，结果这个队竟然排了这么长，哎！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442429" data-seq="278442430" data-pid="278442429" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442429.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/83/wKgBEFpKEYyAYZsiAA2jSH4_ypw42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/83/wKgBEFpKEYyAYZsiAA2jSH4_ypw42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442429" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278442531">
            最后还有一点时间就去琉璃厂遛遛，听我朋友说在这遇到过刘烨老婆，不过我谁都没见到，匆匆就回去拿行李走啦！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442549" data-seq="278442550" data-pid="278442549" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442549.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/85/wKgBEFpKEZGAb5oUAA7Z9cR6AAI38.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/85/wKgBEFpKEZGAb5oUAA7Z9cR6AAI38.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442549" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_278442567" data-seq="278442568" data-pid="278442567" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8164582/278442567.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:680px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/89/wKgBEFpKEZmAPBocAAw-txNuiR805.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CF/89/wKgBEFpKEZmAPBocAAw-txNuiR805.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="278442567" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="278442570">
            好，不写了，我要检票进站了，再见<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>！
        </p>
    
</div>
